 changes'<br>
'the first of which is a modification to the minimum age in which you can join this guild'<br>
'it has been raised from 10 to 20'<br>
'this includes any of your alts as well'<br>
'they must reach their 20th season before membership will be granted'<br>
'there are multiple reasons for this which I can explain on a one off basis if you request it'<br>
'we have opted to begin raids for all seasons'<br>
 'in reality, you should be able to begin raiding starting in your 30th season or so'<br>
'starting in places such as Najena, Kaesora, Splitpaw, etc..'<br>
'your officers and I will begin scheduling these once we further our membership in the individual class levels'<br>
 'so please, keep recruiting'<br>
 'it is very important'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:13:31 2003] Klean tells the guild,in Elvish, 'one question'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:13:36 2003] Sirdo tells the guild,in Elvish, 'sure'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:13:44 2003] Klean tells the guild,in Elvish, 'will i have to leave because i dont qualify the age'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:13:53 2003] Sirdo tells the guild,in Elvish, 'no'<br>
'those how are currently in, stay in'<br>
 'secondly'<br>
'an update on the progress of the guild...'<br>
 'we are still lacking in the pure amount of members that we have across all the seasons of play'<br>
 'therefore, I am going to introduce an incentive plan =)'<br>
'for each member that you bring on that stays with us through a 45 day trial period'<br>
 'you will be rewarded as follows'<br>
'seasons 20 -35 - 100pp'<br>
'seasons 36 - 45 300pp'<br>
'seasons 45+ 500pp'<br>
 'so get recruiting already'<br>
 '=)'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:16:59 2003] Klean tells the guild, 'how many recruiters do we have'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:17:07 2003] Sirdo tells the guild,in Elvish, 'any officer can interview'<br>
 'a new member must get the approval from two officers'<br>
 'and fill out our application'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:17:34 2003] Demidrako tells the guild,in Lizardman, 'every one should be recriuting and passing on to officers'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:17:36 2003] Klean tells the guild, 'ok'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:17:55 2003] Sirdo tells the guild,in Elvish, 'thirdly'<br>
over the past several weeks I have been raiding a lot with an alliance of sort... this alliance will prove usefull for all of us in a higher seasons until we can fill in our ranks -- if your interested in hunting with this alliance, please contact me for details... again, you should be 50+ for this'<br>
 'lastly'<br>
 'I have noticed that a few of you have yet to register on our guild website and our guild message board'<br>
 'all events and most discussion regarding guild business is hosted in one of those two places'<br>
 'it is...'<br>
 'www(dot)chivalrousvalor(dot)com'<br>
*very* important that you register and visit that site reguraly'<br>
 'any questions?'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:22:09 2003] Gwendion tells the guild,in Elvish, 'I registered and all , but I cant find myself on the roster anymore, did something change on the website'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:22:25 2003] Sirdo tells the guild,in Elvish, 'yes, there is a bug in the roster'<br>
 'they are trying to fix it'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:22:52 2003] GUILD MOTD: Kithroch - Please remember to register at our website www.chivalrousvalor.com<br>
[Thu May 01 21:22:58 2003] Sirdo tells the guild,in Elvish, 'ty Kith'<br>
 'any more questions?'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:23:32 2003] Wendolin tells the guild,in Dwarvish, 'One question'<br>
 'About how many folks are curren ly in the guild?'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:23:58 2003] Sirdo tells the guild,in Elvish, 'Press Alt-G'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:24:00 2003] Demidrako tells the guild,in Elder Elvish, '29'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:24:43 2003] Sirdo tells the guild,in Elvish, 'any further questions?'<br>
[Thu May 01 21:25:33 2003] Sirdo tells the guild,in Elvish, 'ok'<br>
